You can view the IIS gui conole by running "Inetmgr" on the commandline.

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

To automate IIS you first need to ensure you have the "webadministration":

&nbsp;

[powershell]
PS C:\Windows\system32> Get-Module -ListAvailable

